# AC-FDL-E2: Unregistered atom literal #FOO -> collapses to #R001
#
# #FOO is a well-formed but unregistered atom name. The atom registry
# resolves it to the #R001 fallback. The script returns a valid :code
# value whose atom name is "R001". Both runtimes produce identical
# toNative output since they share the @rcrsr/rill atom registry.

#FOO
